정리하면:
빌드 결과물 : build/libs/demo-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
Harbor 주소 : 192.168.241.101:30002/base/spring-app
태그        : latest + BUILD_NUMBER
manifest    : deploy/deployment.yaml (같은 레포)
Jenkinsfile 작성할게요:
groovypipeline {
  agent {
    kubernetes {
      yaml """
        apiVersion: v1
        kind: Pod
        spec:
          nodeSelector:
            usage: infra
          containers:
          - name: gradle
            image: 192.168.241.101:30002/proxy-cache/gradle:9.4.1-jdk21
            command: ['sleep', 'infinity']
            resources:
              requests:
                memory: "512Mi"
                cpu: "500m"
              limits:
                memory: "1Gi"
                cpu: "1"
          - name: kaniko
            image: 192.168.241.101:30002/proxy-cache/martizih/kaniko:debug
            command: ['sleep', 'infinity']
            volumeMounts:
            - name: harbor-creds
              mountPath: /kaniko/.docker
          volumes:
          - name: harbor-creds
            secret:
              secretName: harbor-credentials
              items:
              - key: .dockerconfigjson
                path: config.json
      """
    }
  }

  environment {
    HARBOR_URL  = '192.168.241.101:30002'
    IMAGE_NAME  = 'base/spring-app'
    GIT_REPO    = 'https://github.com/fullofnull/myapp.git'
  }

  stages {
    stage('Checkout') {
      steps {
        checkout scm
      }
    }

    stage('Build') {
      steps {
        container('gradle') {
          sh 'gradle clean build -x test'
        }
      }
    }

    stage('Image Build & Push') {
      steps {
        container('kaniko') {
          sh """
            /kaniko/executor \\
              --context=dir://\${WORKSPACE} \\
              --dockerfile=Dockerfile \\
              --destination=\${HARBOR_URL}/\${IMAGE_NAME}:\${BUILD_NUMBER} \\
              --destination=\${HARBOR_URL}/\${IMAGE_NAME}:latest \\
              --insecure \\
              --skip-tls-verify
          """
        }
      }
    }

    stage('Update Manifest') {
      steps {
        container('gradle') {
          sh """
            git config user.email "jenkins@ci.local"
            git config user.name "Jenkins"
            sed -i 's|image: \${HARBOR_URL}/\${IMAGE_NAME}:.*|image: \${HARBOR_URL}/\${IMAGE_NAME}:\${BUILD_NUMBER}|' deploy/deployment.yaml
            git add deploy/deployment.yaml
            git commit -m "ci: update image tag to \${BUILD_NUMBER}"
            git push \${GIT_REPO} HEAD:main
          """
        }
      }
    }
  }

  post {
    success {
      echo "빌드 성공: \${IMAGE_NAME}:\${BUILD_NUMBER}"
    }
    failure {
      echo "빌드 실패"
    }
  }
}
근데 GitHub 레포가 public인가요 private인가요? private이면 git push 단계에서 토큰 인증이 필요해요!입력 내용: publicpublic오전 10:54Claude 응답: public이면 push할 때 인증이 필요해요.public이면 push할 때 인증이 필요해요. 읽기는 되지만 쓰기는 GitHub 토큰이 있어야 해요.
GitHub에서 토큰 발급해주세요:
GitHub → Settings → Developer settings
→ Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)
→ Generate new token
→ 권한: repo 체크
→ Generate token → 토큰 복사
토큰 발급 후 Jenkins에 등록할게요:
Jenkins → Jenkins 관리 → Credentials
→ System → Global credentials → Add Credentials
→ Kind: Username with password
→ Username: fullofnull
→ Password: (발급한 토큰)
→ ID: github-credentials
→ Save
